longBusinessSummary: Ranplan Group AB, a software company, develops, markets, licenses, and sells various software solutions in Asia, North America, Europe, the Middle East, and Africa. It offers Ranplan Professional, a platform that allows users to design and optimize complex in-building and outdoor wireless networks; Ranplan In-Building, an in-building network design tool that incorporates all 5G and Wi-Fi technologies to tackle indoor environments; Ranplan In-Building Lite, an agile tool that enables RF engineers to significantly reduce the time it takes to design networks; and Ranplan Tablet, which automates site surveys and in-building network designs. The company also provides Ranplan licensing plans, which include FlexiLease, a scalable, budget-friendly plan that offers the flexibility to access software without the burden of large upfront costs; FlexiBuy, a phased investment plan that offers timeless value by allowing users to start with a lease and transition to a perpetual license; InfinityPlus, a lifetime access plan with unlimited potential that provides a one-time payment option for unlimited access to the software, unlocking the full potential of network planning needs; and Ranplan Viewer for reviewing 2D and 3D network designs. Additionally, it serves mobile operators, telecommunication equipment vendors, and system integrators to plan, design, and optimize 4G, 5G, and Wi-Fi wireless networks. Ranplan Group AB was founded in 2012 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
